      <title>特朗普对哈里斯的攻击可能让他失去他需要的选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-risks-losing-voters-he-needs-with-loaded-attacks-on-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队正在疯狂地调整其策略，放弃了将前对手乔·拜登描述为软弱的毫无意义的计划，并对比共和党候选人年轻二十岁的卡玛拉·哈里斯测试新的攻击路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-risks-losing-voters-he-needs-with-loaded-attacks-on-harris</guid>
