      <title>商业游说团体称南非经济复苏需要改革推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/south-africa-revival-needs-reform-jumpstart-business-lobby-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非商业领袖协会首席执行官 Busisiwe Mavuso 表示，南非新的多党政府必须优先振兴国营港口、水利和电力网络，并努力实现流程自动化以吸引投资并促进滞后的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/south-africa-revival-needs-reform-jumpstart-business-lobby-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
